query:
insert into nft_auction_bid (
                auction,
                buyer,
                price,
                next_bid_value, 
                created_at,
                tx_lt,
                declined,
                nft,
                nft_owner,
                collection,
                price_token
            )
            select
                unnest($1::varchar[]),
                unnest($2::varchar[]),
                unnest($3::numeric[]),
                unnest($4::numeric[]),
                unnest($5::timestamp[]),
                unnest($6::bigint[]),
                unnest($7::boolean[]),
                unnest($8::varchar[]),
                unnest($9::varchar[]),
                unnest($10::varchar[]),
                unnest($11::varchar[])
